========================================
|ID|OPERATOR            |NAME          |
----------------------------------------
|0 |HASH RIGHT SEMI JOIN|              |
|1 | SUBPLAN SCAN       |SUBQUERY_TABLE|
|2 |  LIMIT             |              |
|3 |   TOP-N SORT       |              |
|4 |    TABLE SCAN      |t1            |
|5 | TABLE SCAN         |t1            |
========================================

